Output example/tapes/output/textarea.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 700
Set Height 400
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

Type "fvm dart run tool/bin/textarea.dill"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "Hello, World!"
Enter
Type "This is a multi-line editor."
Enter
Type "Press Ctrl+C to quit."
Sleep 1s
Ctrl+C
Sleep 500ms
